}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== *"LS51LTSW VER.A" is silkscreened on the board.
===Specifications=== *Processor: [[Marvell]] 98DXH325A2 @333MHz (ARMv5) *Flash/RAM: 128MB (NAND) Flash, 256MB RAM (DDR2) *LAN: 8x Gigabit (RJ45) 802.3at PoE Ethernet ports, :1x GbE SFP slots, :18Gbps switching capacity, Rack mountable (1U, 19") *PoE: 802.3af (PoE), 802.3at (PoE+), 180W PoE budget
